                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A creature damaged by the aluum enforcer's fist Strike must succeed at a <span data-pf2-check=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-traits=\"arcane,incapacitation,necromancy\" data-pf2-label=\"Paralyzing Force DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"27\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span> save or become @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Paralyzed]{Paralyzed} for 1 round. On a critical failure, the creature is paralyzed for [[/r 1d4]]{1d4 minutes} and falls @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Prone]{Prone}.</p>"
