                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The aluum enforcer emits a keening wail in a 15-foot cone that deals [[/r 9d6 #sonic]]{9d6 sonic damage} (<span data-pf2-check=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-traits=\"damaging-effect,arcane,auditory,evocation,mental,sonic\" data-pf2-label=\"Soul Shriek DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"27\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Fortitude</span> save). A creature that fails its save is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Stunned]{Stunned 1}, or @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Stunned]{Stunned 3} on a critical failure.</p>\n<p data-visibility=\"gm\">The aluum can't use Soul Shriek again for [[/br 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>"
